readGraph(String) - Method in interface main.contracts.IGraph
It reads from a file the edges of a graph
and automatically creates the vertices based on the edges
File format:
<\size value>
<\source value> <\destination value>
<...> <...>

Example:
2
1 2
2 1
readGraph(String) - Method in class main.Graph
 
readWeightedGraph(String) - Method in interface main.contracts.IGraph
It reads from a file the edges of a weighted graph
and automatically creates the vertices based on the edges
File format:
<\size value>
<\source value> <\destination value> <\weight value>
<...> <...> <...>
Example:
2
1 2 1.5
2 1 2.5
